jasperReport.name: caizheng
jasperReport.queryString: select DATE_RECEIPT,ASSETS_NUM, ATYPE_CODE, ATYPE_NAME,ASSETS_NAME,MEASURE_UNIT, case when SRCID='0' then '新购' when SRCID='1' then '调拨' when SRCID='2' then '捐赠' when SRCID='3' then '划拨' when SRCID='4' then '置换' when SRCID='5' then '其他' end SRCIDS,DATE_BUILD, case when CGZZXS_ID=1 then '政府集中采购' when CGZZXS_ID=2 then '部门集中采购' when CGZZXS_ID=3 then '分散采购' when CGZZXS_ID=4 then '其他' end CGZZXS_IDS, case when CHANQX_SID=1 then '有产权' when CHANQX_SID=2 then '无产权' end CHANQX_SIDS, case when QUANSXZ_ID=1 then '国有' when QUANSXZ_ID=2 then '集体' end QUANSXZ_IDS, LAND_PHOTO_NAME, CERTIFICATE,DIHAO,DATE_FAZ,AREA_LAND,PARCELLAND_ADDRESS,QCXTZC_NUM, case when VALUE_TYPE=1 then '原值' when VALUE_TYPE=2 then '暂估值' when VALUE_TYPE=3 then '重置值' when VALUE_TYPE=4 then '无价值'end VALUE_TYPES, VALUE_BOOK,VALUE_ORIGINAL,VALUE_FISCAL_ALLOC,BUSINESS_INCOME, YSW_INCOME,OTHER_FUNDS, CZXJY_FUNDS,ACCOUNT_PROOF,AREA_TUDI,AVG_PRICE,USE_DP, case when USE_STATUS=1 then '在用' when USE_STATUS=2 then '未使用' when USE_STATUS=3 then '不需用' when USE_STATUS=4 then '其他' end USE_STATUSES,AREA_ZIYONG,AREA_LEND,AREA_RENT,AREA_INVEST, AREA_DANBAO,AREA_OTHER,VALUE_ZIYONG,VALUE_LEND,VALUE_RENT,VALUE_INVEST,VALUE_DANBAO,VALUE_OTHER,LEND_DF_DP,RENT_DF_DP,DESCRIPTION, OPERATOR,AUDITOR,case when ACCOUNTED='Y' then '已入账' when ACCOUNTED='N' then '未入账' end ACCOUNTED,NOTHANDLE,a.sum_area FROM sc_parcelland,(select sum(area_tudi) as sum_area from sc_parcelland) a
